### Test Filtering & Sorting API

# Set your JWT token here
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### 1. Get emails with default sorting (newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get emails sorted by date (oldest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?sortBy=date&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get emails sorted by date (newest first)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Filter unread emails only
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?unread=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Filter emails with attachments only
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?hasAttachments=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Filter unread emails with attachments
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?unread=true&hasAttachments=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Sort by subject (A-Z)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?sortBy=subject&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Sort by subject (Z-A)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?sortBy=subject&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Sort by sender email (A-Z)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?sortBy=sender&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Combined: Filter unread + Sort by date (newest)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?unread=true&sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. Combined: Filter with attachments + Sort by date (oldest)
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?hasAttachments=true&sortBy=date&sortOrder=asc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. All filters + sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/mailboxes/INBOX/emails?unread=true&hasAttachments=true&sortBy=date&sortOrder=desc
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
